		<element kind="textField" uuid="8ebd051e-606e-4c43-8438-1a90279e46f2" x="1" y="84" width="378" height="8" forecolor="#8C1915" fontSize="6.0" bold="true" hTextAlign="Center" vTextAlign="Middle">
			<expression><![CDATA["Thank you, " + $F{name} + " for choosing " +$F{reg_name}]]></expression>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="3a073146-84f2-41db-a6dc-a998563c47cb" x="1" y="14" width="379" height="70" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[• Kindly collect your spectacles within 30 days from the invoice date. Uncollected orders may be cancelled after this period.
• Spectacles will be issued once the full payment has been completed.
• Frame adjustments and minor repairs are offered as a service; however, they are done at the customer’s discretion and risk.
• Orders are custom-made and therefore cannot be cancelled once confirmed.
• A fully paid invoice serves as an official payment receipt.
• If an advance payment is made, this invoice will be considered a receipt for the advance amount.
• As most items are custom-made, returns and cash refunds are not available.
• Exchanges or store credit may be offered in accordance with our store policy.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="974c9d9b-1e71-4293-a623-476aecf3427d" x="4" y="0" width="229" height="13" fontSize="7.0" bold="true" hTextAlign="Left" vTextAlign="Bottom">
			<text><![CDATA[Dear Valued Customer,]]></text>
		</element>
